data.description: All renovated MOVE IN READY  charming 3-bedroom, 1-bath  in Wildwood, Florida,  just a few miles to  the villages.    This beautifully all  renovated home has a brand-new AC unit and new water heater.    The kitchen are all renovated with new  granite countertops , new cabinets , new appliances, new  flooring and fresh paint throughout.      With three spacious bedrooms with also new carpets and a large renovated bathroom.    Very large indoor laundry room and one car garage with plus  huge backyard with nature trees.      NO HOA, NO CDD.    Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to own a turnkey and all renovated  property, perfect for a starter home or a income rental Property.
